Package: flexIC
Type: Package
Title: Flexible Rank-Preserving Correlation Engine
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Kevin", "Wells", email = "kevin.e.wells@usm.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a fast, flexible method for simulating continuous variables with specified rank correlations using the Iman-Conover transformation and back-ranking. Includes plotting tools and error diagnostics.
